WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.700
Okay.

2
00:00:01.720 --> 00:00:03.620
I'm about to rest, too.

3
00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:06.340
It's time to get back to the company, Dad.

4
00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:08.400
Take care of your health first.

5
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.640
Wait until it's completely finished before coming back.

6
00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:12.780
Don't worry, there will be absolutely no problem with me here.

7
00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:17.300
Then I'll be at home waiting for your good news.

8
00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:19.940
Wait until the new landmark project is photographed.

9
00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.340
I'll go celebrate for you.

10
00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.900
Then we have a deal.

11
00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:29.940
Your father-in-law works for you during this time, waiting for the project to end.

12
00:00:30.120 --> 00:00:31.360
I'll give him credit.

13
00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:32.580
Really.

14
00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:34.720
You can mention anything you want.

15
00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:35.760
You know that.

16
00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:38.520
What do I really want most?

17
00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.360
I think the one I want most is you.

18
00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:42.740
It's you.

19
00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:44.840
Lots of people here.

20
00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.840
When the project is over, I will agree with you.

21
00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:48.700
Really.

22
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:53.940
So if there's nothing, I'm leaving.

23
00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:58.940
She's too easy to fool.

24
00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:08.260
You're awake.

25
00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:09.640
Go.

26
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.980
Don't watch, there will be many opportunities later.

27
00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:17.700
Let's have breakfast first.

28
00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:28.060
The completed project was a big surprise.

